"1/2 cup mayonnaise","3 tablespoons brined capers, rinsed and coarsely chopped","4 teaspoons Dijon mustard","4 teaspoons chopped fresh dill","2 teaspoons fresh lemon zest","8  large hard-cooked eggs, peeled and chopped","  Kosher salt and pepper","4  brioche buns or other large, soft round buns, sliced crosswise and lightly toasted","1/2 cup thinly sliced radishes","4  leaves green-leaf or romaine lettuce"